      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "waste"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是浪费，表示时间、钱或精力没有被好好使用。朋友看到空袋子，就说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It's a waste of time."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 53,
      "start": 417.687,
      "end": 429.159,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "waste"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但要记住，这是朋友的判断，不是故事的全部真相。朋友觉得没有鱼就是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a waste of time"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，他自己觉得安静的上午很值得。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 54,
      "start": 429.509,
      "end": 432.477,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "realize"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "realize"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 55,
      "start": 432.826,
      "end": 434.578,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
