      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "realize"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是意识到、明白过来。它常常表示“之前没看懂，现在终于懂了”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 57,
      "start": 442.606,
      "end": 452.53,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "realize"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "They don't realize one important thing."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "朋友没有意识到真正的重点：他不是为了鱼，他是为了坐在船上安静一会儿。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 58,
      "start": 452.88,
      "end": 462.588,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "grammar"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不要从一大张表开始。先听这篇课文反复出现的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "-ing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "节奏。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 59,
      "start": 462.937,
      "end": 473.157,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一组："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "without catching anything"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "without"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "后面接"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "catching"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，意思是“没有钓到任何东西”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 60,
      "start": 473.507,
      "end": 484.962,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二组："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Instead of catching fish"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "instead of"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "后面接"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "catching"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，意思是“不是钓鱼，而是钓到别的东西”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 61,
      "start": 485.312,
      "end": 498.992,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三组："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "After having spent whole mornings on the river"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "after"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "后面可以接一个"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "-ing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "短语，表示“在做完这件事之后”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 62,
      "start": 499.342,
      "end": 514.745,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四组："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "interested in fishing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "interested in sitting in a boat and doing nothing"
