        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "interested in"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "后面常接"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "-ing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，因为这里说的是活动和兴趣。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 63,
      "start": 515.095,
      "end": 526.991,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你可以这样记："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "without + -ing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "instead of + -ing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "after + -ing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "interested in + -ing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 64,
      "start": 527.341,
      "end": 537.541,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这套语法刚好也指向主题：他不是在数鱼，他是在说一种活动、一段过程、一种让自己安静下来的兴趣。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 65,
      "start": 537.89,
      "end": 554.25,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "还有两个小表达。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "not even"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“甚至连……都不”，所以"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "not even old boots"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "很好笑。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "at all"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "用来加强“什么也不”的感觉："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "doing nothing at all"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 66,
      "start": 554.6,
      "end": 563.6,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "好，把今天的故事放进自己的生活。想一个你喜欢做的活动，它不一定有很亮眼的结果，但过程本身让你舒服。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 67,
      "start": 563.95,
      "end": 576.209,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以是慢慢搭"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "LEGO"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，在"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Minecraft"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "里乱建房子，安静画画，散步，练琴，投篮，拍照片，或者放学后坐一会儿。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 68,
      "start": 576.559,
      "end": 588.719,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "关键句型是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I am not really interested in ___. I am only interested in ___ and ___ ."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 69,
      "start": 589.069,
      "end": 597.897,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你还可以加一句对比："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "My friends think it is a waste of time, but they don't realize that I enjoy ___."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
